754
00:54:03,628 --> 00:54:04,628
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau ingin pergi ke UKS,
atau ke rumah sakit?</i></font>

755
00:54:04,628 --> 00:54:06,184
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa aku pergi ke rumah sakit?</i></font>

756
00:54:06,184 --> 00:54:07,797
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa Ji Soo baik-baik saja?</i></font>

757
00:54:07,797 --> 00:54:10,614
